WEBVTT

1
00:00:23.907 --> 00:00:29.767
Zhang confesses his crime in court. A flashback shows him leaving a dark room.

2
00:00:29.767 --> 00:00:35.627
Xuechun walks across a small garden bridge at night.

3
00:00:35.627 --> 00:00:41.487
Xuechun pauses on the garden path, looking around.

4
00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:04.795
Hearing Zhang's clapping, Xuechun opens the door.

5
00:01:04.795 --> 00:01:10.640
Zhang enters behind her. Seeing no one, Xuechun closes the door.

6
00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:16.485
In the next scenes, noticing the man, Xuechun thinks it is Mr. Lin and talks with him.

7
00:01:16.485 --> 00:01:22.330
Zhang covers his face and quickly exits; Xuechun watches.

8
00:01:22.330 --> 00:01:28.175
Zhang stumbles at the gate, revealing his face.

9
00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:39.550
In the next scenes, Zhang grabs Xuechun, stabbing her with a knife.

10
00:02:13.375 --> 00:02:16.825
Back in the court, Zhang looks up and smiles.


